<h3>Match Content Length to SERP Competition</h3>
<p>There is no universal "ideal" word count. The right length is whatever beats the top 3 ranking pages.</p>
<p>Check the top 5 results for your keyword. Note the average word count. Aim for 20 to 30% longer, but only if the additional content adds genuine value. Padding with fluff hurts rankings.</p>
